IS_PIT, made by SKAR.

---

An Ice Skating map based on The Pit levels from the Mortal Kombat series.
Best played with sv_airaccelerate 300.

---

Ice Skating is still a very new maptype, "ice skating" works like airstrafing.
You use A and D to strafe while at the same time turning in that same direction to gain speed.

---

You spawn with a knife in an invisible box. After 3 seconds the box will break and you will be able to skate. It is recommended that you dont jump or duck while in the box because you might end up not hitting the boost on the ground properly.
In the center of the map you will find a flashbang which will respawn every 10 seconds.
After 2 minutes you will be unable to iceskate and will have to walk normally, this is so the round doesnt last too long.

---

Custom skybox by Karatekaefer

---

Please enjoy!

Is_Curve Map by Apexi Skybox by Karatekafer Background:An ice skating map inspired by Jack The Stripper's Is_Jump. Note it is 100% made my me except the skybox. This is not a rip or copy from any map what so ever. Each team spawns in a dome-like room and in the middle there is a Gravity lift. There is two ways to get up to the top. The gravity lift or the teleport in spawn. Call it a race if you wish to get to the shotguns. Warning: Do not copy ANYTHING from this map without proper credits or permission. Do not decompile this map and take something from it. If you do you will be hunted down! Custom red glass texture by me. Interested in using it? Message me. Want to see more maps like this? Visit Mapjunkies.com and add us to your watchlist! Enjoy

Is_ctf_revolution

by ZaLoS

custom textures by Icecreamlock, ZaLoS

custom skybox texture by Karatekaefer

3d skybox by udel steve

Ctf prefab by ZaLoS


CTF:

You cant pick up your own flag, which is located behind spawn.

To score get the other teams flag and drop it at your flags base. You cannot score without your flag being at the base. Scoring kills the other team.



The map:
There are three routes, the middle is the fastest, but prolly the hardest to stay on. The south is easier than the middle and includes some wall obstacles and is meant for the newer is-ers. The northern route is an upper route that is the slowest but will take you directly to the opposites team flag.

There are two shotties, one at each teams base. They are intended for defensive use tho you could go offense with them. However, I Would recomend sticking one teammate on D tho.


Special thanks to www.solidsurf.info, www.fpsbanana.com, www.mapjunkies.com, and Icecreamlock for hosting the beta! 

Additional thanks to Apexi for the ctf+is idea :D

Is_arena is the second map of the Ice Skating maptype. The first being is_stadium by HellraisedSurfer. A word of advice before you try this map out, you need sv_airaccelerate around 300 or you wont airstrafe very well. To IceSkate you must jump out of spawn until you start hovering over the ice. Then you airstrafe in slaloms, circles etc so you pick up speed and knife eachother. It takes a while to get used to but it gets very fun when you know what you are doing. The custom geometry took me a very long time to produce, but I think it was worth it! Map took 3-6 hours to make and 3 minutes to compile. There were 2 beta tests and many changes have been made to the map since it was first thought of. Please rate my map fairly and if you don't understand the maptype or how to IceSkate please do not rate this map low! Textures in this map are all custom and are by me excluding the skybox which is by Karatekaefer. Check his skybox textures out! Here's a video of the gameplay for those who need it! Note: The textures that I made in this map are on my FPSB page! We are looking for decent and beginner mappers, texture makers and artists... mapjunkies.com
